{"title":"Centos 安装 sqlServer","num_read":1728,"num_like":648,"num_collection":313,"num_comments":172,"slug":"resource-DB-SQLServer-Centos-sqlServer","date":"2021-03-15T16:00:00.000Z","img":"/img/header_img/tools/centos.png","_id":"clhrbp2av001po5lgfowo3l7u","project":"DB","site":{"data":{}},"updated":"2022-08-05T04:18:36.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/resource-DB-SQLServer-Centos-sqlServer.json","webPath":"2021/03/16/resource-DB-SQLServer-Centos-sqlServer/","permalink":"https://sunfy9.gitee.io/2021/03/16/resource-DB-SQLServer-Centos-sqlServer/","excerpt":"CentOS安装sqlServer","covers":null,"keywords":"sunfy, hexo-theme-snail","content":"<p>CentOS安装sqlServer<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"下载\"><a href=\"#下载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载\"></a>下载</h3><p>Microsoft SQL Server Red Hat 存储库配置文件：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -o /etc/yum.repos.d/mssql-server.repo https://packages.microsoft.com/config/rhel/7/mssql-server-2017.repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"通过yum安装\"><a href=\"#通过yum安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过yum安装\"></a>通过yum安装</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install -y mssql-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行\"><a href=\"#运行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行\"></a>运行<sunfy-line></h3><p>运行包安装完成后mssql conf 安装并按照提示操作以设置 SA 密码，并选择你的版本，安装完成后会自动启动数据库服务。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/opt/mssql/bin/mssql-conf setup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注意，这一步需要选择所要安装的数据库版本和管理员sa账户密码，请按照实际需求选择版本，并记住所设置的密码。</p>\n<h3 id=\"查看是否启动成功\"><a href=\"#查看是否启动成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看是否启动